SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?country) AS ?count) WHERE {
  ?country a <http://www.wikidata.org/ontology#Country> .
  
  # Democracy index value triple
  ?country ?democracyIndexProperty ?democracyIndexValue .
  
  # The property should be related to Democracy Index entity
  ?democracyIndexProperty <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?label .

ASK WHERE {
  ?place <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P276> <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q39> .
  ?place <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P625> ?coord .
  
  # Extract coordinate string
  BIND(STR(?coord) AS ?coordStr) .
  
  # Remove "Point(" prefix and ")" suffix
  BIND(STRAFTER(?coordStr, "Point(") AS ?coordNoPrefix) .
  BIND(STRBEFORE(?coordNoPrefix, ")") AS ?coordClean) .
  
  # Extract latitude (second number)
  BIND(STRDT(STRAFTER(?coordClean, " "), xsd:decimal) AS ?latitude) .
  
  FILTER(?latitude > 47.8)
}

  ?album <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Album> ;
         <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/artist> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_(band)> ;
         <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?releaseDate .

}

SELECT DISTINCT ?countryLabel ?headOfStateLabel WHERE {
  VALUES ?country { 
    <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q183> 
    <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q142> 
  }
  
  # For Germany: direct head of state
  {
    FILTER(?country = <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q183>)
    ?country <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P35> ?headOfState .
  }
  UNION
  # For France: indirect pattern
  {
    FILTER(?country = <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q142>)
    ?instance <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P31> ?country .
    ?instance <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P527> ?part .
    ?part <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P35> ?headOfState .
  }
  
  # Get the label of the country
  OPTIONAL {
    ?country <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?countryLabel .
    FILTER (lang(?countryLabel) = "en")
  }
  
  # Get the label of the head of state
  OPTIONAL {
    ?headOfState <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?headOfStateLabel .
    FILTER (lang(?headOfStateLabel) = "en")
  }
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wdtn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct-normalized/>
PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?character) AS ?count) WHERE {
  ?character a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/FictionalCharacter> .
  
  # Gender filter: either literal "female" or resource Female
  ?character <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/gender> ?gender .
  FILTER(
    ?gender = "female"@en || 
    ?gender = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Female>
  )
  
  # Swordfighter filter: occupation or category
  {
    ?character <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/occupation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swordfighter> .
  }
  UNION
  {
    ?character <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Swordfighters> .
  }
}

PREFIX wdata: <http://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Special:EntityData/>
PREFIX wdno: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/novalue/>
PREFIX wdsubgraph: <https://query.wikidata.org/subgraph/>

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wdtn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct-normalized/>
PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?company ?companyLabel ?inceptionDate WHERE {
  VALUES ?companyKnown { <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2905359> }
  
  # Get inception date for Black Diamond Equipment
  ?companyKnown <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P571> ?inceptionDateKnown .
  
  # Find La Sportiva entity by label
  ?company rdfs:label ?companyLabel .
  FILTER(LCASE(?companyLabel) = "la sportiva")
  ?company <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P571> ?inceptionDateLaSportiva .
  
  # Bind the two companies and their inception dates
  {
    BIND(?companyKnown AS ?company1)
    BIND(?inceptionDateKnown AS ?date1)
    BIND(?company AS ?company2)
    BIND(?inceptionDateLaSportiva AS ?date2)
  }
  
  # Compare dates and select the earlier one
  BIND(IF(?date1 < ?date2, ?company1, ?company2) AS ?company)
  BIND(IF(?date1 < ?date2, ?inceptionDateKnown, ?inceptionDateLaSportiva) AS ?inceptionDate)
  
  # Get label for the selected company
  ?company rdfs:label ?companyLabel .
  
  FILTER(LANG(?companyLabel) = "en")
}
LIMIT 1
